track_notes: Park near spot height 382 on the moorland road. Visit the Wainwright Outlyers of Buck Barrow (LDO-009),Burn Moor (LDO-010) and Kinmont Buck Barrow (LDO-012) en-route if you wish.
From parking at Ulpha.  It is possible to park approx 0.5 miles further up the road at the edge of the woodland.
